modName: Face Presets GOT Margaery Tyrell (Natalie Dormer)
descriptionHtml:
Face Presets for Natalie Dormer as Margaery Tyrell in GOT.

Requirements: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Race Menu[/url]

Mods used: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2356/?]XCE[/url] and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52322/?]WSCO
[/url]Presets was made in vanilla, mods used are just the visual to look better.

Bugs: Complexion, face and lip color might be in a different index.
Just set: Complexion=0
             Hair Color=3 or 4 Bright blond or any of your Choice
             Eye Shadow and eye tint=1
             Lough lines=1
             Cheek and Cheek lower=1
             Nose, Chin, Neck and Forehead=1
             Lip=2

Enjoy. . . :D
author: Haunted1994
